      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIS FERNANDO (8) goes very well this trip starting 30 times for 10 wins and nine minors. Missed the frame latest (20.43) when seventh over 340m at this track in a NG. Looks suited here and rates on top. MIDNIGHT MACK (2) finished third (20.07) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 7th there. Has a good record here at this journey. Has performed well from this box with a win and six minor placings to his name from nine starts. Cannot be underestimated. MICK THE MASTER (5) has a strong record this trip with 24 wins and 17 placings from 56 starts. Below best last time at this track (20.02) in a Mix 1/2/3, finishing a 5.5 lengths fifth. Looks one of the chances. SWEET BEVELY ANN (1) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
